    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u1EA5y c\xF3 c\xE2y v\u1EA3 b\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng, Ng\xE0i b\u01B0\u1EDBc l\u1EA1i g\u1EA7n xem nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EA5y tr\xE1i n\xE0o, ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 l\xE1 th\xF4i. Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu b\u1EA3o c\xE2y v\u1EA3, \"M\u1EA7y s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD ra tr\xE1i n\u1EEFa.\" C\xE2y v\u1EA3 li\u1EC1n ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4. "), mdx("h6", {
