  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c m\xF4n \u0111\u1EC7 th\u1EA5y v\u1EADy v\xF4 c\xF9ng s\u1EEDng s\u1ED1t. H\u1ECD h\u1ECFi, \"T\u1EA1i sao c\xE2y v\u1EA3 ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4 nhanh nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy?\" "), mdx("h6", {
