  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu c\xE1c con tin th\xEC c\u1EA7u xin \u0111i\u1EC1u g\xEC c\u0169ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\u1EA3.\"C\xE1c nh\xE0 c\u1EA7m quy\u1EC1n nghi ng\u1EDD quy\u1EC1n n\u0103ng c\u1EE7a Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu \u0111i v\xE0o \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD. Trong khi \u0111ang d\u1EA1y d\u1ED7 th\xEC c\xE1c gi\u1EDBi tr\u01B0\u1EDFng t\u1EBF v\xE0 c\xE1c b\xF4 l\xE3o \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p Ng\xE0i. H\u1ECD h\u1ECFi, \"Th\u1EA7y l\u1EA5y quy\u1EC1n n\xE0o m\xE0 l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng vi\u1EC7c n\u1EA7y? Ai cho th\u1EA7y quy\u1EC1n \u1EA5y?\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu \u0111\xE1p, \"T\xF4i c\u0169ng h\u1ECFi c\xE1c \xF4ng m\u1ED9t c\xE2u. C\xE1c \xF4ng tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi t\xF4i th\xEC t\xF4i s\u1EBD n\xF3i cho c\xE1c \xF4ng bi\u1EBFt t\xF4i l\u1EA5y quy\u1EC1n n\xE0o m\xE0 l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng vi\u1EC7c n\u1EA7y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c \xF4ng h\xE3y cho t\xF4i bi\u1EBFt: Khi Gi\u0103ng l\xE0m b\xE1p-t\xEAm cho d\xE2n ch\xFAng th\xEC l\u1EC5 \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EEB Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF hay t\u1EEB ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta?\" H\u1ECD b\xE0n lu\u1EADn v\u1EC1 c\xE2u h\u1ECFi Ng\xE0i nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF n\u1EA7y, \"N\u1EBFu ch\xFAng ta n\xF3i, 'L\u1EC5 b\xE1p-t\xEAm c\u1EE7a Gi\u0103ng t\u1EEB Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF \u0111\u1EBFn,' th\xEC \xF4ng ta s\u1EBD h\u1ECFi, 'T\u1EA1i sao c\xE1c \xF4ng kh\xF4ng tin \xF4ng \u1EA5y?' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF2n n\u1EBFu ch\xFAng ta n\xF3i, 'L\u1EC5 \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EEB ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta' ch\xFAng ta s\u1EBD b\u1ECB qu\u1EA7n ch\xFAng ph\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED1i v\xEC ai c\u0169ng tin Gi\u0103ng l\xE0 nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn h\u1ECD tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi, \"Ch\xFAng t\xF4i kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt.\" Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu b\u1EA3o h\u1ECD, \"V\u1EADy t\xF4i c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng n\xF3i cho c\xE1c \xF4ng bi\u1EBFt t\xF4i l\u1EA5y quy\u1EC1n n\xE0o m\xE0 l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng vi\u1EC7c n\u1EA7y.\"Ng\u1EE5 ng\xF4n v\u1EC1 hai con trai "), mdx("h6", {
